{"tid":1686841,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【炒車】【屯門不明氣體】分析數據 前天文台長料礦山村有可疑","createTime":"2019-11-01T11:48:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T11:54:53.000Z","uid":86199,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7f7e106c1a93375be79b204069414ae4bfdd30be","tid":1686841,"uid":86199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T11:48:33.000Z","msg":"屯門區本周一（28日）多處發現懷疑刺鼻氣味，港府雖然積極跟進，但暫未查到氣味來源。天文台前台長林超英根據資料分析後，則認為不明氣體來源不是警方的大興行動基地，而是位於西北方更遠位置，有可能是屯門北面礦山村一帶。<br />\n<br />\n林超英在昨日發表的網誌中指，「事發當晚屯門有人在沒有科學調查之下，指是警察秘密放催淚煙，聚眾鬧事，結果搞到真的要放催淚煙驅散，現在梳理資料之後，顯示不明氣體來自他處，當日到街上鬧事的人不知有何感想？」<br />\n<br />\n他指，「凡事必須用常識和道理去分析，才決定應對行動，切要避免先入為主，或者被怨憤和仇恨蒙蔽心思，否則容易做錯事，將來後悔莫及。」<br />\n<br />\n林超英網誌全文連結：<br />\n<a href=\"https://tiandiyouqing.blogspot.com/2019/10/blog-post_31.html?fbclid=IwAR1ScLqHKeNFbuB0UUbVWATM7DDHv_py-pDVkAFRq6kgzFrSqjxHNIXeui4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftiandiyouqing.blogspot.com%2F2019%2F10%2Fblog-post_31.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1ScLqHKeNFbuB0UUbVWATM7DDHv_py-pDVkAFRq6kgzFrSqjxHNIXeui4&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvFLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=80134c33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tiandiyouqing.blogspot.com/2019/10/blog-post_31.html?fbclid=IwAR1ScLqHKeNFbuB0UUbVWATM7DDHv_py-pDVkAFRq6kgzFrSqjxHNIXeui4</a>"},{"pid":"2f9183c2d55e5b2de9ed90da866d2f135b441e29","tid":1686841,"uid":293667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T11:49:30.000Z","msg":"【白宮聯署 】依個就快截止⚠️<br />\n1. 制裁TVB<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/32jy4fj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F32jy4fj&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvFLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=07bc379c\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/32jy4fj</a><br />\n尚欠60000人聯署，11月9日截止。<br />\n2. 解散警隊<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/31gWPHR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F31gWPHR&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvFLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=21d1467b\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/31gWPHR</a><br />\n尚欠 16000 人聯署，11 月 9日截止。<br />\n簽&gt